210
00:55:25.170 --> 00:55:27.715
Jævler!

211
00:55:48.360 --> 00:55:50.613
Faen!

212
00:55:52.072 --> 00:55:54.575
Faen.

213
00:55:56.744 --> 00:56:01.540
Skjending.
