216
00:56:16.513 --> 00:56:18.849
Faen ta dere!

217
00:56:18.933 --> 00:56:24.772
Det er så vakkert, men
hvis de finner olje... Katastrofe.


218
00:56:24.855 --> 00:56:30.235
